## Citation

If you use these datasets, please cite the original papers:

**PHEME:**
> Zubiaga, A., et al. (2016). Analysing how people orient to and spread rumours in social media. PLoS ONE.

**Twitter15/16:**
> Ma, J., et al. (2017). Detect rumors in microblog posts using propagation structure via kernel learning. ACL 2017.

**Weibo:**
> Ma, J., et al. (2016). Detecting rumors from microblogs with recurrent neural networks. IJCAI 2016.
